# BOINC
Use docker containers to run the boinc client and also run the boinc CLI

## BOINC client
github.com/laurentmalvert/docker-boinc

## BOINC command line tool
github.com/laurentmalvert/docker-boinccmd

## BAM - BOINC account manager
Connect to your BAM account (https://boincstats.com/en/bam/) in order to manage your
projects
